{"tid":2227903,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"理想既烏托邦應該係點 (求各行人士埋黎吹吹)","createTime":"2020-10-03T07:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T10:56:52.000Z","uid":372525,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"249d63026d520572d6eaa87cfcbe519251707060","tid":2227903,"uid":372525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:04:38.000Z","msg":"如果突然有個地方俾大家由零開始 建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以21世紀既科技同道德觀念，呢個國家應該係點?<br />\n<br />\n想集思廣益吹下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設:<br />\n1. 土地不受限制<br />\n2. 大陸架上海島嶼<br />\n3. 無淡水供應<br />\n4.赤道附近<br />\n5.會打風<br />\n6. 一年4季都30度up<br />\n7.每日日照由朝早6點至晚上8點<br />\n8.外交上與大部份國家都FD,但係冇國家提供軍事保護(冇外國駐軍)<br />\n<br />\n拋下磚先<br />\n<br />\n經濟:<br />\n<img src=\"https://ec.europa.eu/jrc/sites/jrcsh/files/styles/normal-responsive/public/agriculture-waste-water-adobestock_86772407.jpeg?itok=-jSsAmyT\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fjrc%2Fsites%2Fjrcsh%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fnormal-responsive%2Fpublic%2Fagriculture-waste-water-adobestock_86772407.jpeg%3Fitok%3D-jSsAmyT&h=9ad60eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國內農業 做到自給自足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高度自由既法例，common law , 支持科研公司生根，data centre 業務<br />\n出口高科技農業，醫療旅遊，data centre services 賺外匯<br />\n稅制做到有效既財富再分配，加部份國家既投資支援社會福利，唔以賣地支持公共開支<br />\n<br />\n電力，水源.<br />\n[url]<img src=\"https://images.theconversation.com/files/41263/original/56464frd-1392126197.jpg?ixlib=rb-1.1.0&amp;q=45&amp;auto=format&amp;w=1200&amp;h=1200.0&amp;fit=crop\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F41263%2Foriginal%2F56464frd-1392126197.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26q%3D45%26auto%3Dformat%26w%3D1200%26h%3D1200.0%26fit%3Dcrop&h=6f0cd484&s={SIZE}\" />[/url]<br />\n有pump storage 支持，base load 以風，太陽能支持，peak load 由小量天然氣機組頂。<br />\n需求方面要有嚴格同aggressive demand side management，例如限制每戶peak hours 唔可以用多過某個數既電。<br />\n淡水由海水化淡供應，同樣地會有嚴格既demand side management , 沖涼用水會有限制<br />\n<br />\n社會體制<br />\n<img src=\"https://kpbs.media.clients.ellingtoncms.com/assets/img/2020/06/24/ap_20087639706912_wide-7bd46adc386fda5d8a04e6b3160f084196076f2d_t800.jpg?90232451fbcadccc64a17de7521d859a8f88077d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkpbs.media.clients.ellingtoncms.com%2Fassets%2Fimg%2F2020%2F06%2F24%2Fap_20087639706912_wide-7bd46adc386fda5d8a04e6b3160f084196076f2d_t800.jpg%3F90232451fbcadccc64a17de7521d859a8f88077d&h=a723f173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n採取 國家精英主義規劃，由真。精英去plan 點run 國家，俾小量空間市民義政。 <br />\n有機制可以起得到大部份市民支持下俾國民組織既議會介入國家行政，起確保精英行政之下唔會出現小數人既暴政(不過要諗避免市民被不當影響無限挑戰國家行政)<br />\n<br />\n社會福利<br />\n<img src=\"https://montsame.mn/files/5df1c1f6d366d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmontsame.mn%2Ffiles%2F5df1c1f6d366d.jpeg&h=fa3d8771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n房屋一律由國家建造，以人數，住戶年齡等情況分派。 <br />\n兩人家庭 唔小於1000 呎，3 人唔小於1500呎，如此類推。<br />\n一人住戶需入住如青年旅社般既公共房屋，並需有理由支持想一人住。<br />\n<br />\n醫療由國家保障基本醫療，傷風感冒 自己起屋企休息<br />\n<br />\n國家支持 基本9年免費教育( 小一至中三) ，中三後可決定接受 vocational training / 繼續上<br />\n<br />\n其餘有free internet access<br />\n<br />\n返工有標準工時，每日計埋食飯唔可以做多過10 小時，專業人士每做50小時要有3小時做低技術工人做既野。每人每個月要有5小時社區服務時數，掃下街，做下好似公務員既part time <br />\n<br />\n公共治安:<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6f/Tokyo_Metropolitan_Police_Department_Toyota_Crown_Patrol_Car_GRS214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F6%2F6f%2FTokyo_Metropolitan_Police_Department_Toyota_Crown_Patrol_Car_GRS214.jpg&h=87fc45dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公共治安由專業警察 混合普通市民既民警執法，有電槍,冇槍。<br />\n<br />\n軍隊同樣由全職同後備民兵組成，每個市民都要每10年服1年兵役，全民皆兵<br />\n<br />\n軍備有防衛武器，如愛國者地對空飛彈系統，反艦導彈，魚雷艇。<br />\n<br />\n想知再講"},{"pid":"08b0dc878096dc9e1e474ab86e2aecff373975b5","tid":2227903,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:09:52.000Z","msg":"每個市民都要每10年服1年兵役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19801ad09df93693c57ed4b6027b54ed6d8c944","tid":2227903,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"Brave New World 其實幾痴線幾正，仲要program到啲人做緊苦差都樂在其中"},{"pid":"5fab1e25173ba8fc2ee8e4f81485e384af249f1f","tid":2227903,"uid":71508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:17:13.000Z","msg":"烏托邦=On9<br />\nSomeone has to suffer<br />\nBut that one is not me"},{"pid":"8c25db791c6ca8d027a2101700b78eef01265a7a","tid":2227903,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f19801ad09df93693c57ed4b6027b54ed6d8c944","tid":2227903,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"Brave New World 其實幾痴線幾正，仲要program到啲人做緊苦差都樂在其中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:19:47.000Z","msg":"好似而家嘅支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋一啲都唔正，同任人魚肉有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff25028855c29fa2627a8a697ea3fc6620d9b997","tid":2227903,"uid":324629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"建議樓主等夜晚先出呢個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361656bce146427240e7745d8580db9ce0a13dd2","tid":2227903,"uid":2429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:21:01.000Z","msg":"樓主係共產主義恐怖份子。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673110cafe95bd6ec4524354b71ff6b0e7afa3a1","tid":2227903,"uid":50060,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:26:58.000Z","msg":"完全無人類"},{"pid":"bc67a7698eeb56eb055014b0b94831bad76c78bd","tid":2227903,"uid":372525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08b0dc878